title: 2000 Arizona Census Places
name: 2000 Arizona Census Places
description: This is Arizona Places for 2000 from the TIGER/Line Shapefiles.  Places includes Census Designated Place, CDP, City, Village, and Town.  The TIGER/Line Shapefiles are an extract of selected geographic and cartographic information from the Census MAF/TIGER database.  The Census MAF/TIGER database represents a seamless national file with no overlaps or gaps between parts.  However, each TIGER/Line Shapefile is designed to stand alone as an independent data set or the shapefiles can be combined to cover the whole nation.
